quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad"
  7,2,"Ko Deftere Jippinaande e maa…óa, wata …ďitteende wonu ka …ďernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonannde gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  7,3,"Jokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wata on jokku gaanin …óum, weldii…ďe, fan…óii ko waajitoto…óon"
  7,4,"∆äuu…óii e ca'e …óe Men halki! Lepte Amen …óen ari e majje jemma hi…ďe waalii …óaanii, maa hara ko …ďe fowtii…ďe √Īalorma"
  7,5,"Noddaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun …ďaawo lepte Amen …óen arde …ďe, wonaano si naa wi'ugol : \"Menen men laatino too√Īoo…ďe"
  7,6,"Ma Men Lamnditoyo …ďen …ďe (Men) Nulunoo e mun, Ma Men Lamnditoyo kadi Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  7,7,Ma Men Fillanoroyo …ďe (golle ma…ď…ďe …óen) e ganndal. Men wonaano wirnii…ďe
  7,8,"Manndakke=peesgol …óen nde √Ďalnde, ko …óe goonga. Kala mo manndake (mo∆ī∆īi …óen) teddi, ko …ďen …óon woni maloytee…ďe …ďen"
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (mo∆ī∆īi) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko …ďen …óon woni sooyinir…ďe pittaali mu'un sa…ďu ko …ďe laatinoo hi…ďe yedda Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  7,10,"Gom…óii Men Newinanii on ke leydi, Men Wa…óani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) fan…óii ko yettoton"
  7,11,"Gom…óii Men tagii on, refti Men Mbaadini on, refti Men Wi'ani Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen : \"Sujjanee Aadama\", …ďe sujji, si wanaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujju…ďe …ďen"
  7,12,"O Daali : \"Ko ha…óu-maa nde sujjataa nde Mi Yamir-maa?\" O wi'i : \"Mi…óo …ďuri mo mo∆ī∆īude : A Tagii lam immorde e Yiite, A Tagii mo immorde e loopal"
  7,13,"O Daali : \"Jippo ton, haananaama nde mawnintinto…óaa ton. Yaltu, an ko a jeyaa…óo e hoy…ďe …ďen"
  7,14,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Nennitanam haa √Īalnde …ďe immintintee"
  7,15,"[Alla] Daali : \"An, ko a jeyaa…óo e nennitantee…ďe …ďen"
  7,16,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Sabu ko bewinir…óaa lam kon, ma mi joo…óano …ďe ka laawol Maa focciingol"
  7,17,"Refti mi ardiranay …ďe yeeso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, e ka e √Īaame ma…ď…ďe e ka nane ma…ď…ďe. A tawataa ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko yettoo…ďe [Ma]"
  7,18,"[Alla] Daali : \"Yaltu ton, ko a Ňči√Īaa…óo ra…óaa…óo. Kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ď…ďe, ma Mi hebbiiroy Jahannama onon denndaangal"
  7,19,"Ko an yo Aadama, ho…óu an e …ďeyngu maa ka Aljanna, √Īaamee kala nokku ka yi…óu-…óon ; wata tun on …ďa…óto ngal …óoo leggal, sakko laato…óon e too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  7,20,"Seytaane sowinsini …ďe, fii yo o fe√Ī√Īinan …ďe ko suu…óaa e ma…ď…ďe e awraaji ma…ď…ďe, o wi'i : \"Joomi mon ha…óiraali on ngal leggal si wanaa fii wata on laato Malaa'ika maa laato…óon duumotoo…ďe [ka Aljanna]"
  7,21,"O woondani …ďe o wi'i : \"Min ko mi laa…ďanoo…ďe on"
  7,22,"O hodiri …ďe janfa. Nde …ďe mee…óunoo laggal ngal, awraaji ma…ď…ďe …óin fee√Īani …ďe, …ďe wa…óti hi…ďe surritora kaaki Aljanna …óin. Joomi ma…ď…ďe noddi …ďe : \"E Mi ha…óaano on e ngal leggal, Mi wi'ani on : Pellet, seytaane ko ga√Īo mo'on …ďanngu…óo"
  7,23,"∆Āe wi'idi …ďe …ói…óo : \"Joomi amen, men too√Īii ko'e amen. Si A haforanaali men yurme…óaa men, ma men jeye e sooyu…ďe …ďen"
  7,24,"[Alla] Daali : \"Jippee (ka leydi), yoga mon ko ay…ďe yoga. Hino woodani on ka leydi ton √Īii…ďirde e dakamme haa saanga"
  7,25,"[Alla] Daali : \"Ko (ka leydi) ton wuuroton, ko ton kadi maayoton, ko e mayri kadi yaltinoyte…óon"
  7,26,"Ko onon yo …ďi…ó…ďe Aadam! Gom…óii Men Jippinii e mo'on conci surray…ói awraaji mon …óin e cu…óaari. -Ko cocni kulol …óin non …ďuri mu∆ī∆īude.- Ko …óum jeyaa…óum e Aayeeje Alla. Belajo'o, kam…ďe …ďe waajitoto"
  7,27,"Ko onon yo …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama! Wata seytaane fitinir on wano o yaltinirnoo baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen ka Aljanna, himo …ďoora e ma…ď…ďe conci ma…ď…ďe …óin fii yo hollu …ďe awraaji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Pellet, himo reeni on kanko e gorol makko ngol nokku ka on yi'ataa …ďe. Menen Men wa…óii seytaaneeji …óin weldii…ói …ďen …ďen gom…óintaa"
  7,28,"Si …ďe wa…óii pankare, …ďe wi'a : \"Men tawru …óum baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen, ko Alla yamiri men …óum\". Maaku : \"Pellet, Alla yamirtaa pankare. E on wowlay e hoore Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,29,"Maaku : \"Joomi am yamirii nun…óal. √Ďii…ďnon geece mon …óen nokku kala e ka juuloton, tororon Mo la…ď…ďinangol Mo diina kan. Ko wano O Fu…ó…óori on non ruttirton"
  7,30,"Fedde goo O fewnii, fedde goo majjere nden jojji e hoore ma…ď…ďe. Kam…ďe …ďe jogitike seytaaneeji …óin weldii…ďe gaanin Alla, kam…ďe hi…ďe sikka ko …ďe feewu…ďe"